Horrible idea...<P>And heres why.<P>1) then you could have a level 50 pet AND Mind flay. this is too much.<P>2) or you could have a level 50 pet and both your highest stacking DOTs, also too much.<P>3) And here si the biggest reason... it is a band aid approach. It slightly remedys the situation, but not not cure the cause. We don;t need to be able to ignopre mind, like so many have matter for so long. Then how varied woudl Sorcerors be? Not all all. They woudl ALL be full body, the rest matter.<P>The mind line needs to be made better. Just like I have always said we can not just ingore matter since so many thought it useless, we need to make the line worthwhile, not abandon them. Taking the one or two good abilities out of a line and stuffing them in the good line does nto help. It lessens the options for the class, and turns them into clones.<P>So we need to make Mind betetr. We need to make all the lines viable, across all levels of play.<P>--------------------<P>i3ullseye<BR>"You're good, but me? I'm Magic!"<P>Rictus -Sorceror(DAOC)/Rictus(EQ)<BR>DAOC Sorceror team lead...<P>Please visit our <A HREF="http://www.yesterdayland.com/popopedia/shows/toys/ty1050.php" TARGET=_blank>Sponsors!</A>  <IMG SRC="biggrin.gif" border="0">
