Actually Bull it is a good idea BECAUSE of 1 and 2.  <P>Make the matter spec dot AOE - matter is now viable.<P>Leave body the way it is - body is now viable.<P>The only reason to spec mind now is if you want a pet - or you want a gimped mez.  Move the charm to base line.  Anyone that has been in RvR battles knows the pet is only good until the first time you are killed.  In the place of the charm, add an AOE unmezz line to mind:<P>Level 12 - Radius of 100<BR>Level 24 - Radius of 200<BR>Level 36 - Radius of 300<BR>Level 48 - Radius of 400<P>Make it so it only affects those your level or below.<P>Now Bards are unique primary CC because they have insta-ranged mez, speed, rez, and heal.<P>Healers are unique primary CC because they have insta-ranged mez, stun, and pb mez and stun, heals, and rez.<P>Sorcerers (if they spec high mind) can have a great AOE unmez.<P>--------------------<P>Malachai Mindbender<BR>Sorcerer of Avalon<BR>Guinivere
